---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About | juanalytics">
  <section style="padding: 4rem 0;">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px;">
      <h1 style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">About Me</h1>

      <div style="line-height: 1.8; font-size: 1.1rem;">
        <p>
          Hello! I'm Juan Manuel Perafan, an Analytics Engineer based in Utrecht, Netherlands.
          Since 2017, I've been passionate about data analytics, visualization, and building
          modern data stacks that empower organizations to make better decisions.
        </p>

        <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">What I Do</h2>
        <p>
          I specialize in analytics engineering with a focus on:
        </p>
        <ul style="margin-left: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
          <li>Data transformation and modeling with dbt</li>
          <li>Modern data stack architecture</li>
          <li>Data visualization and storytelling</li>
          <li>Building and nurturing data communities</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Recognition & Community</h2>
        <p>
          I'm honored to have received the <strong>dbt Community Award in 2024</strong> for
          my contributions to the analytics engineering community. I'm deeply involved in
          organizing and fostering data communities:
        </p>
        <ul style="margin-left: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
          <li><strong>Official Amsterdam dbt Meetup</strong> - Organizer (Dec 2022-Present)</li>
          <li><strong>Analytics Engineering Meetup</strong> - Organizer (Feb 2021-Nov 2024)</li>
          <li><strong>Netherlands Data Visualization Meetup</strong> - Organizer (Jul 2019-Present)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Published Author</h2>
        <p>
          I co-authored <strong><a href="https://www.amazon.com/author/jmperafan" target="_blank">Fundamentals of Analytics Engineering</a></strong>,
          a comprehensive guide to building end-to-end analytics solutions with modern tools and best practices.
          The book covers everything from dbt fundamentals to advanced analytics workflows, helping data professionals
          transition into analytics engineering or level up their existing skills.
        </p>

        <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Conference Speaking</h2>
        <p>
          As a <strong>Distinguished Toastmaster</strong> since 2016, I've honed my communication
          skills through competitive speaking. I've won multiple speech competitions including
          the German International Speech Contest. I regularly speak at major data and analytics
          conferences including:
        </p>
        <ul style="margin-left: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
          <li><strong>Coalesce</strong> (dbt's annual conference)</li>
          <li><strong>Linux Foundation OS Summit</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Big Data Summit Warsaw</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Dutch Big Data Expo</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Developer Week Latin America</strong></li>
        </ul>

        <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Background</h2>
        <p>
          Born and raised in Colombia, I relocated to the Netherlands in 2011. My journey into
          analytics began in 2017, and I discovered dbt in 2020. Attending Coalesce 2021 was
          transformative and deepened my involvement in the dbt community.
        </p>

        <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Languages</h2>
        <p>
          I'm multilingual with native/bilingual proficiency in <strong>English</strong> and
          <strong>Spanish</strong>, and professional working proficiency in <strong>German</strong>.
        </p>

        <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Let's Connect</h2>
        <p>
          I'm always excited to connect with fellow data enthusiasts, speak at events,
          or collaborate on interesting projects. Feel free to reach out!
        </p>

        <div style="margin-top: 2rem; display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap;">
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jmperafan/" target="_blank" class="button">LinkedIn</a>
          <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@juanalytics" target="_blank" class="button">YouTube</a>
          <a href="https://linktr.ee/juanalytics" target="_blank" class="button">Linktree</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/jmperafan" target="_blank" class="button">GitHub</a>
          <a href="https://sessionize.com/jmperafan/" target="_blank" class="button">Speaking Profile</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
